Like all of the courses in the Google Digital Marketing Specialization, the information is well presented and easy to digest.  The supplemental learning materials and readings will help you master the subjects and are absolutely required if you want to learn more than superficially.  This particular class covers many topics that most consumers will be well aware of without having ever taken a marketing class!  There is a section devoted to setting up a mock store on Shopify that was quite interesting. This class is a solid 4 out of 5, with a deduction of one star because I think that the presentations should be available for simplified note taking.
